comments: Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Richardson's (PHI) path and does not deliver any contact.
Thybulle (PHI) makes marginal contact to Nurkic's (POR) arm as he steals the pass.
Richardson (PHI) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Thybulle (PHI) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) head and affects his driving shot attempt.
Horford (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path.
McCollum (POR) maintains a legal defensive position as he contest Burks' (PHI) play at the basket.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Thybulle's (PHI) path.
Burks (PHI) legally contest Trent Jr.'s (POR) jump shot attempt.
Horford (PHI) makes marginal contact with Nurkic (POR) during the drive to the basket.
Nurkic (POR) brings his arm down and makes contact to Horford's (PHI) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) makes marginal contact with Horford's (PHI) lower body as he legally blocks Horford's driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) briefly grasps Harris' (PHI) arm during the rebound.
Thybulle (PHI) legally contest Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) makes hand to ball contact as Burks' (PHI) secures the rebound.
Anthony (POR) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Horford (PHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Scott (PHI) commits a take foul on Nurkic (POR).
Anthony (POR) grabs Richardson's (PHI) jersey as he moves off-ball prior to the ball being released during the inbound play.
Anthony (POR) makes marginal leg to leg contact with Richardson (PHI) on the release of his dribble.
Anthony (POR) maintains a legal defensive position on Richardson's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Harris (PHI) briefly engages then disengages with Trent Jr. (POR) during the rebound. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Lillard (POR) makes hand to ball contact and dislodges the ball from Harris (PHI) during the rebound.
